ŠFrom Phil to Alina, my wife and love of my life.
For memories of lunches and moments shared
in Berkeley Square Mayfair and in
the London Town that we grew to love together
and call our home."─
┴Here is where good friends should meet
To laugh and talk on Sammy's seat
In loving memory of
Samantha Jane Thompson 1981 - 2009
She brought laughter into our lives
and love into our hearts"╚
┼[LEFT]
Angel
Occasionally, we are graced with the presence of an
earth bound angel. They are unable to stay with us for
long, but while they do, they bring unexpected joy
and happiness to all they touch.

[RIGHT]
Eva
07-10-2001  ~ 07-12-2003
Chasing pigeons, feeding ducks, in spite of illness 
living every moment"╩
ŪPercy Charles (Tony) LeBaigue, born in Primrose Hill
A much loved husband, father and grandfather
who dedicated his life to family and work
Self proclaimed genius and inventor - a very amusing man"╠
